snippet.title: Core Open Alpha Trailer: Welcome to the Multiverse
snippet.description: Welcome to the Multiverse, our trailer announcing the Open Alpha for Core. Core is a platform for creating and playing games. All footage in the trailer is from games hosted on Core that you can play for free right now. https://www.coregames.com/
